Whenever one thinks of having momos, WOW Momo is the place to order from.. They have a wide range of options for momos from vegetarian or non-vegetarian options...steamed/fried or pan-fried... Different preparation.. U can choose from a variety of price options.. There is also an option of Moburg which is available in veg and non veg options which is just yummy..
